<br>
This server is FULL of roleplayers, and many many of the ones who aren't WILL roleplay if you get the ball rolling with humor, warmth, and kindness.<br>
<br>
Just remember that half of &quot;roleplay&quot; is &quot;play&quot;! It's a pleasure, not an onerous duty.<br>
<br>
